      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Martin Sedlak</b>\n</p><p><b>Martin Sedlák</b>, <br />\na Czech software engineer and computer chess programmer. He began chess programming in 2006 and his <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant engine <a href=\"/Cheng\" title=\"Cheng\">Cheng</a>, hosted by <a href=\"/index.php?title=Emil_Vlas%C3%A1k&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Emil Vlasák (page does not exist)\">Emil Vlasák</a>, represents about three years of development <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>. \nMartin Sedlák is further author of the <a href=\"/TLCS-TLCV\" title=\"TLCS-TLCV\">TLCV</a> client <b>livius</b> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>, along with <b>Cheng4</b> available at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/GitHub\">GitHub</a> under the permissive <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zlib_License\">zlib license</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Sedlak&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Sedlak&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=36870\">search or transposition table bug?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 30, 2010</li></ul>\n<p><b>2011</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=38760\">Stockfish random generator (rkiss.h)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 15, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a>, <a href=\"/Bob_Jenkins#RKISS\" title=\"Bob Jenkins\">RKISS</a> by <a href=\"/Bob_Jenkins\" title=\"Bob Jenkins\">Bob Jenkins</a>, <a href=\"/Pseudorandom_Number_Generator\" title=\"Pseudorandom Number Generator\">PRNG</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39340\">UCI multipv question</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 11, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2012</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=43864\">microsecond-accurate timing on Windows</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 28, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Windows\" title=\"Windows\">Windows</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44111\">VisualStudio - __fastcall instead of __cdecl?</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 18, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/C\" title=\"C\">C</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=44841\">OT: denormals</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Float\" title=\"Float\">Float</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?topic_view=threads&amp;p=490492&amp;t=45846\">Re: Move Tables - explain as if I'm five</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 04, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/Table-driven_Move_Generation\" title=\"Table-driven Move Generation\">Table-driven Move Generation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=46040\">Optimizing bitboards for ARM</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 17, 2012&#160;» <a href=\"/BitScan\" title=\"BitScan\">BitScan</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2013</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=46780\">A few questions about CECP</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 05, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=46968\">DrMemory: memory debugger tool for Windows (and Linux)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 22, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Memory\" title=\"Memory\">Memory</a>, <a href=\"/Debugging\" title=\"Debugging\">Debugging</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=47318\">A few positions to test movegen</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 24, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=49351\">nullmove verification vs avoid null</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 14, 2013&#160;» <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li></ul>\n<p><b>2014</b>\n</p>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51110\">Cheng4 0.36c - last version</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 30, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52133\">livius sources (a TLCV-compatible client)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 26, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/TLCS-TLCV\" title=\"TLCS-TLCV\">TLCV</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Sedlak&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55000\">cheng4 0.38 release</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 18, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55188\">Lazy SMP in Cheng</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 02, 2015&#160;»  <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56201\">[OT] LOC counting tool</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 02, 2015 <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=56858\">thread affinity</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 03, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Thread\" title=\"Thread\">Thread</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=66121\">AlphaZero performance</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 25, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/AlphaZero\" title=\"AlphaZero\">AlphaZero</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=5&amp;t=67407\">Real names</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 10, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=69046&amp;start=1\">Re: CCR board representation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 25, 2018&#160;» <a href=\"/Nibble#ArrayOfNibbles\" title=\"Nibble\">Array of Nibbles</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Sedlak&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=7&amp;t=73082\">scan-cut slider attack generation</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 13, 2020 &#160;» <a href=\"/Bitfoot#ABBitboards\" title=\"Bitfoot\">A/B Bitboards</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Sedlak&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/kmar\">kmar · GitHub</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/kmar/cheng4\">GitHub - kmar/cheng4: cheng4 chess engine</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/kmar/livius\">GitHub - kmar/livius: livius - a Qt-based TLCV-compatible live chess viewer</a> </li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.vlasak.biz/cheng/\">Cheng chess engine</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Martin_Sedlak&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.vlasak.biz/cheng/\">Cheng chess engine</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52133\">livius sources (a TLCV-compatible client)</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Martin Sedlak</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 26, 2014</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/kmar\">kmar · GitHub</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Source_lines_of_code\">Source lines of code from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301105603\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.011 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.011 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 92/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 194/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\